---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="The Project" lang="en" currentPath="/en/project">
  <section style="padding:4rem 1.5rem;max-width:860px;margin:0 auto;">
    <p style="color:var(--gold);font-size:0.8rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.12em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:0.5rem;">The Project</p>
    <h1 style="font-family:'Source Serif 4',Georgia,serif;font-size:clamp(2rem,4vw,2.8rem);font-weight:700;color:var(--ink);margin:0 0 1.5rem;">Uganda: Education in Adjumani Refugee Settlement</h1>
    <p style="color:var(--stone);font-size:1.1rem;line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:2rem;">Adjumani in northern Uganda hosts one of Africa's largest refugee settlements — around 240,000 people, mostly from South Sudan. For most children, education is the only way out of this cycle.</p>
    <p style="color:var(--stone);font-size:1.1rem;line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:2rem;">A full scholarship covers everything: school fees, boarding, books, and uniform — € 900 per year, per child.</p>
    <a href="/en/donate" style="background:var(--teal);color:#fff;padding:14px 28px;border-radius:8px;font-weight:700;text-decoration:none;font-size:1rem;display:inline-block;">Fund a scholarship</a>
  </section>
</Layout>
